  "title": "Citrusy Creamy Ukrainian Pinto Bean Bowl",
  "description": "A spring-inspired Ukrainian dish featuring pinto beans, served in a stone bowl with a citrusy twist, perfect for a brunch mood. This shojin-friendly recipe is both refreshing and filling.",
