  "instructions": [
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook for 3 minutes until translucent.",
    "Add the grated carrots and cook for 2 minutes until they start to soften.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the lemon juice, orange juice, and a pinch of salt and pepper.",
    "Add the cooked pinto beans, chopped dill, and cooked carrot mixture to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Stir in the vegan sour cream until well combined.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the bean mixture in a stone bowl, garnished with additional chopped fresh dill if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
